9.	Given that radius is 2 and area is calculated as 12.5678, 
use string format operators to print the values of the variables radius and area so that the output looks like this:
Radius is: 	          2
Area is:	  12.57
# code:
  area = 12.5678
  print ("%.0f"%radius,"%.2f" % area)
