 10.	What are the values of the following expressions, assuming that p is 17 and q is 18?
       i.	p // 10 + p % 10
       ii.	p % 2  + q % 2
       iii.	 (p + q) // 2
       iv.	 (p + q) / 2.0
       
       
       # code :
        p = 17
        q = 18
        
        i = p // 10 + p % 10
        print (i)
        
        ii = p % 2  + q % 2
        print (ii)
        
        iii = (p + q) // 2
        print (iii)
        
        iv = (p + q) / 2.0
        print (iv)
        
        >>>  8
        >>>  1
        >>>  17
        >>>  17.5
       
        
        

  
